Introduction

Lee Chaeyoung is a South Korean dancer, rapper, singer-songwriter under ASND. She was one of the main dancers and the lead rapper of the girl group fromis_9.

In 2017, Chaeyoung appeared and competed in the show "Idol School" where she ranked 4th with 65,318 votes, earning a spot in the group fromis_9.

Chaeyoung debuted as a member of fromis_9 on January 24, 2018, with the mini album To. Heart.
